Vulkan is a low-level, low-overhead cross-platform API
and open standard for 3D graphics and computing. It
was intended to address the shortcomings of OpenGL,
and allow developers more control over the GPU.

add these

export PATH=/opt/bin:/opt/include:$PATH
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/lib64:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH
export VK_LAYER_PATH=/opt/share/vulkan/explicit_layer.d:$VK_LAYER_PATH
